Children.Text:
Cultivar names include several codes for several traits.
* RR = Roundup Ready - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance for Glyphosate herbicide.
* CL = Clearfield - These cultivars as developed for the Clearfield Canola weed control system.
* TT = Triazine Tolerant - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance for triazine herbicide
* RT = Triazine and Roundup - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance to both triazine and glyphosate herbicides.
